titlealts.searchtitle: Data Element: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (SICKLE CELL DISEASE) - Description

div.p: NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (SICKLE CELL DISEASE) is the same as attribute NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS.
NEWBORN BLOOD SPOT TEST OUTCOME STATUS CODE (SICKLE CELL DISEASE) is the result of screening for Sickle Cell Disease (SCD).
